not_on_netflix.title: Not on Netflix
not_on_netflix.description: Find them on Tubi day or night — you won’t find these on that other site.

289816.title: Ghost In The Shell
289816.description: See the groundbreaking original before the release of the live-action remake starring Scarlett Johansson! It is 2029 and a female cyborg hunts a hacker who robs humans of their memories.

300166.title: In The Mix
300166.description: A popular DJ finds himself in the middle of a Mafia power struggle after a chance encounter lands him a job as a bodyguard for a mob boss’ daughter.

303190.title: The Usual Suspects
303190.description: The lone survivor of a heist-gone-wrong tells the feds how it all went down as they search for the enigmatic crime lord behind the disaster.

306917.title: The Arrival
306917.description: An astronomer discovers intelligent alien life, but the aliens are keeping a deadly secret and will do anything to keep him from learning the truth.

312200.title: Uptown Girls
312200.description: When her inheritance is stolen, a rock 'n' roll heiress must take a job as a nanny to an 8-year-old girl who is more of an adult than she is.

313931.title: Stir of Echoes
313931.description: After being hypnotized, Tom (Kevin Bacon) is haunted by terrifying visions that seem to be sending him a message from beyond.

316461.title: Hard Candy
316461.description: A 14-year-old girl turns the tables on her would-be predator in this psychological thriller.

321874.title: The Way of the Gun
321874.description: In a case of mistaken identity, two criminals kidnap the surrogate mother to a wealthy couple and all hell breaks loose.

341526.title: Mars
341526.description: Mark Duplass stars in Mars. The discovery of life on Mars places a robotic expedition and a manned mission in a race to the Red Planet. On the way we discover that love - biological, spiritual, and even mechanical - can flourish in all kinds of ways.

345782.title: Jin-Roh (Subtitled)
345782.description: The animation made by famous studio Production I.G! Police member Kazuki Fuse fights anti-government activists. Haunted by images of a girl he saw commit suicide, he gradually learns of a sinister plot in this thriller that was recognized at the Fantasia International Film Festival

355916.title: Daydream Nation
355916.description: Seventeen-year-old Caroline (Kat Dennings) finds herself entangled in a love triangle between her classmate and her high school teacher (Josh Lucas).

396732.title: Short Term 12
396732.description: Grace, a young supervisor at a foster care facility for at-risk teenagers, takes on the crises of two new residents while going through her own.

440278.title: Eddie Griffin: You Can Tell 'Em I Said It
440278.description: The excitable comic again proves why he is one of the world’s premiere funnymen, ripping into racial stereotypes, Viagra, the First Lady, and more.

442415.title: Cherry
442415.description: An Ivy League freshman gets an unexpected education when he falls for an older woman and her 14-year-old daughter develops a crush on him.

448987.title: Last House on the Left
448987.description: Two girls are tortured and left to die after they become captives of four prison escapees who end up facing off with one of the girls' mothers.

453678.title: Frontera
453678.description: When a Mexican worker illegally crosses the US border and is accused of murdering an ex-lawman’s wife, the lives of two families are forever changed.

453766.title: Not Quite Hollywood
453766.description: Explore how Australian filmmakers unleashed a full-frontal explosion of sex, violence, horror and action onto unsuspecting audiences in the '70s.

456876.title: Bad Lieutenant: Port of Call New Orleans
456876.description: In the wake of Hurricane Katrina, a detective investigates the murders of several Senegalese immigrants.

456901.title: Trespass
456901.description: When thieves invade the upscale home of a clever diamond dealer and his wife and take them hostage, the captives must rely on their wits to survive.

456927.title: Labor Pains
456927.description: A young woman with reason to be worried about her professional future hatches a plan where she pretends to be pregnant to avoid being fired.

461002.title: Pusher
461002.description: When Frank is nearly busted delivering a supply of heroin and dumps the drugs, he is goes to desperate measures to make money to pay the buyer back.

461819.title: The Job
461819.description: Unemployed and eager to marry his girlfriend, a man takes a job from a drifter but realizes he may be out of his depth when it turns out to be a hit.

461857.title: Sushi Girl
461857.description: After six years of doing time in silence, an ex-con is treated to a lavish sushi dinner by those he protected, but old wounds are bound to open.

461993.title: Pusher II
461993.description: Tonny is released from prison—again. This time he has his mind set on changing his broken down life, but that proves easier said than done.

462423.title: I Melt With You
462423.description: An annual reunion for a group of college buddies, now in their forties, spirals out of control as each man unravels for his own personal reasons.

462815.title: Barry Munday
462815.description: Barry Munday, a wanna-be ladies' man, wakes up in the hospital after a freak accident to discover he’s missing his “family jewels.” To make matters worse, Barry learns he's facing a paternity lawsuit filed by a woman he doesn’t even remember. Follow this hilarious and heart-warming tale of a guy who finds it took losing his manhood to be a better man.

464397.title: Meadowland
464397.description: In the hazy aftermath of an unimaginable loss, Sarah and Phil become increasingly unhinged and recklessly ignore the repercussions of their behavior.

465289.title: Stone
465289.description: A prison official and a scheming inmate's lives become dangerously intertwined when the convict's seductive wife comes asking for favors.

465292.description: A young electrician assumes a dead man's identity and unwittingly finds himself trapped in an underworld game of Russian roulette.

465321.title: The Extra Man
465321.description: A flamboyant, penniless playwright takes in a young writer who enjoys cross-dressing and teaches him how to survive as an escort for wealthy widows.

465655.title: The Life Before Her Eyes
465655.description: In this intense drama, two high school girls held captive by a gunman are forced to make the terrifying choice as to who will live and who will die.

466199.title: The Trials of Cate McCall
466199.description: An alcoholic lawyer, fighting to recover custody of her daughter, is ordered to defend a woman appealing what might be a wrongful murder conviction.

472182.title: Escape From Planet Earth
472182.description: When a heroic astronaut from a blue-alien planet gets trapped on notoriously dangerous Earth, his overly-cautious brother must rescue him.

472908.title: Odd Thomas
472908.description: In a small desert town, a fry cook with psychic gifts, his girlfriend, and the sheriff team up to stop a weird stranger from unleashing an evil force.

476644.title: The Boondock Saints
476644.description: Irish brothers try to clean up Boston’s underworld by knocking off gangsters and become local folk heroes, as an FBI agent traces their bloody trail.

486060.title: Listen Up Philip
486060.description: When a self-obsessed novelist (Jason Schwartzman) has problems with his novel and his girlfriend (Elisabeth Moss), he seeks refuge in his mentor's cottage where the peace and quiet allow him to focus on his favorite subject - himself.

489706.title: Puncture

489721.title: Wake of Death
489721.description: After an enforcer for a crime mob wants out, his wife is murdered, and his children vanish, thrusting him into a war against the Chinese underworld.

492257.title: Capsule
492257.description: In the early days of the Space Race, a British astronaut finds himself stranded beyond Earth, and mixed up in a conspiracy he doesn't understand.

493084.title: Life on the Line
493084.description: With a huge storm barreling down on their hometown, a team of brave linemen risk it all to make sure essential services stay online.

493370.title: The Whole Truth

494157.title: A Little Bit of Heaven
494157.description: An irreverent young woman, who shields her heart with humor, has a life-altering visit with her doctor, who takes her on an eye-opening adventure.

496328.title: Dolemite
496328.description: Dolemite is the role that made Rudy Ray Moore a midnight-cult-film icon as a framed pimp who fights city corruption with his all-girl Kung-Fu killers.

496332.title: Petey Wheatstraw

496950.title: Nailed!

497358.title: Cake

499311.title: Down Terrace

499563.title: Starry Eyes

555632.description: The Angels must race against a mysterious “Angel gone bad” to retrieve information that could compromise witnesses under federal protection.

555843.title: Tyler Perry's Daddy's Little Girls

565851.description: After discovering a mysterious brush that brings his paintings to life, Ma Liang becomes the target of a ruthless general who yearns for power.

583794.description: A sharp detective duo search for the culprit who killed the son of a New York City Chinatown godfather with the help of a global team of sleuths.
